creator: ChirashiSaumonAvocat
descriptionHtml:
Biloba permet à tous les parents d'échanger avec des professionnels de santé tous les jours de 8h à 22h.


• CHAT MÉDICAL ? •
Nous n'avons pas tous un professionnel de santé dans notre entourage à qui poser nos questions d'ordre médical concernant nos enfants.

Biloba c'est l'application la plus simple pour vous mettre vous, parents, en relation avec un professionnel de santé en quelques minutes. Posez tous types de questions et soyez rassurés sans vous déplacer.

• UN ABONNEMENT SANS CONTRAINTE •
Biloba, c'est un abonnement unique de 5,99€ par mois ou 34,99€ par an pour une équipe médicale toujours à vos côtés :
- Posez toutes vos questions pour tous vos enfants
- C'est sans engagement : vous arrêtez quand vous voulez

• UNE ÉQUIPE MÉDICALE POUR VOUS •
Notre équipe de médecins généralistes, pédiatres et infirmier.e.s puériculteurs/trices vous répondent tous les jours de 8h à 22h.

• 100% SÉCURISÉ •
Biloba respecte à la lettre toutes les obligations du RGPD ainsi que sur la sécurisation de vos données. Ces données sont hébergées sur un serveur certifié par le ministère de la santé (certification dite "HDS" : hébergement de données de santé).

• 100% INDÉPENDANT •
Biloba est une application INDÉPENDANTE. Nous ne sommes en lien avec aucune entreprise de l'industrie pharmaceutique.
Biloba n'affichera jamais de publicité dans l'application. Personne ne peut ainsi rémunérer Biloba pour mettre en avant ses produits ou ses idées.

• PRÉCAUTIONS D'UTILISATION •
Biloba n'est pas un service d'urgence. En cas d'urgence, contactez le 15.

• CONDITIONS D'ABONNEMENT •
Le tarif de 5,99€ par mois ou 34,99€ par an s'applique aux abonnés dans l'Union Européenne. Il peut varier pour les autres pays et les frais réels peuvent devoir être convertis dans votre devise locale selon votre pays de résidence.

L'abonnement sera automatiquement renouvelé à moins qu'il ne soit désactivé dans les paramètres de votre compte Google Play au moins 24 heures avant la fin de la période en cours.
Vous pouvez accéder aux paramètres de votre compte Google Play pour gérer votre abonnement et désactiver le renouvellement automatique. Votre compte Google Play sera débité lorsque l'achat sera confirmé.

• EN SAVOIR PLUS •
Nos conditions d'utilisation : http://terms.bilo.ba
Notre politique de confidentialité : http://privacy.bilo.ba

title: Biloba - Consultez maintenant

creator: Biloba
descriptionHtml:
Biloba is the #1 pediatrics app where every parent can talk to health professionals every day from 8am to 10pm.


Biloba provides on-demand diagnosis, advice and consultation from board-certified pediatricians, GPs and nurses - all via secure, in-app messaging. No appointment, no travel, available every day from 8am to 10pm.
Our team of GPs, paediatricians and nurses is getting back to you in less in a few minutes.

• FREE TRIAL •
Each of our subscriptions start with a free trial of several days. You will be able to ask as many questions as you want during this period. It can be canceled anytime.

Once the free trial period is over, we offer two auto-renewing subscription options: $8.99 per month or $34.99 per year. Our medical team will be on your side during this entire period. You will be able to do unlimited consultations for any of your children. Again, no commitment: you can cancel anytime.

• SECURED IN-APP MESSAGING •
Biloba is fully HIPAA compliant. All your data and conversations are securely stored on our HIPAA databases.

• BILOBA IS NOT AN EMERGENCY SERVICE •
In case of emergency, call 112.

• SUBSCRIPTION PRICING AND TERMS •
Biloba offers an auto-renewing monthly subscription at $8.99/month and an auto-renewing yearly subscription at $34.99/year to provide you with unlimited access to Biloba while you maintain an active subscription.

Payment will be charged to the credit card connected to your App Store Account when you confirm the initial subscription purchase. Subscriptions automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current subscription period. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and the cost of the renewal will be identified. You may manage your subscription and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to your Account Settings after the purchase. Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when you purchase a subscription, where applicable.

• READ MORE ABOUT OUR TERMS & PRIVACY •
Terms: http://terms.bilo.ba
Privacy policy: http://privacy.bilo.ba

Biloba is the #1 pediatrics app where every parent can talk to health professionals every day from 8am to 10pm.


Biloba provides on-demand diagnosis, advice and consultation from board-certified pediatricians, GPs and nurses - all via secure, in-app messaging. No appointment, no travel, available every day from 8am to 10pm.
Our team of GPs, pediatricians and nurses is getting back to you in less in a few minutes.

• PRESCRIPTIONS •
Our doctors might send you prescriptions for your children at the end of the consultation. They are signed electronically & tamper-proof. They will be available right through the app, and will be accepted in all the pharmacies in France.

• SECURED IN-APP MESSAGING •
Biloba is fully HIPAA compliant. All your data and conversations are securely stored on our HIPAA databases.

• BILOBA IS NOT AN EMERGENCY SERVICE •
In case of emergency, call 112.

• SUBSCRIPTION PRICING AND TERMS •
Biloba offers auto-renewing subscriptions to provide you with unlimited access while you maintain an active subscription. Our medical team will be on your side during this entire period. You will be able to do unlimited consultations for any of your children. No commitment: you can cancel anytime.

Payment will be charged to the credit card connected to your App Store Account when you confirm the initial subscription purchase. Subscriptions automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current subscription period. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and the cost of the renewal will be identified. You may manage your subscription and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to your Account Settings after the purchase.

• READ MORE ABOUT OUR TERMS & PRIVACY •
Terms: http://terms.bilo.ba
Privacy policy: http://privacy.bilo.ba


Questions? Let us know at hello@bilo.ba

title: Biloba - On-demand pediatrics

creator: Biloba
descriptionHtml:
Biloba is the 1st Pediatrics On-Demand app that connects all parents to a pediatrician without appointment, any day and by instant messaging. They can ask all the questions they have regarding their children, in addition to the traditional medical follow-up.

HOW DOES IT WORK?
Biloba's messaging works like any traditional instant messaging app: parents write down their questions, and in less than 10 minutes a doctor or nurse take them in charge and will provide them with reliable and personalized answers.
Please note, Biloba is not an emergency service. In case of emergency, call 112.

WHEN AND WHY CAN WE USE BILOBA?
All parents have questions about their kids health and development.  For all these questions, Biloba provides them with a team of general practitioners, pediatricians and nurses, every day from 8 a.m. to 10 p.m.

For instance, it’s possible to use Biloba if your child has a fever, a headache, a stomach ache, reflux or pimples.
But it can also be practical questions about:
- food diversification,
- your baby's breastfeeding,
- your child's sleep,
- the evolution of your child's weight and height,
- a burn,
- a treatment follow-up,
- questions about a vaccine,
- the little daily worries...

If you have any doubt before asking your question, please remember that above all there are no silly questions, and that other parents have undoubtedly asked them before you.
We are here to help you. Feel free to ask anything you have in mind.

WHAT ARE BILOBA'S KEY FEATURES?
With the Biloba app you can:
- Talk to our medical team 7 days a week, from 8 a.m to 10 p.m,
- Send pictures and videos,
- Use one and only subscription plan for all of your children,
- Talk to our medical team wherever you are, whatever you’re doing,
- Get a prescription if needed (only accepted in France).

SUBSCRIPTION PRICING AND TERMS
Biloba offers you automatically renewed subscriptions giving you unlimited access to its services. A medical team will be by your side during the chosen period, and you will be able to consult for all your children. No commitment: you can cancel anytime.

The rates apply to subscribers in the European Union. It may vary for other countries and actual charges may need to be converted to your local currency depending on your country of residence.
The subscription will automatically renew unless it is deactivated in your Store account settings at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.
You can go to your Play Store account settings to manage your subscription and turn off auto-renewal. Your Store account will be charged when the purchase is confirmed.

READ MORE ABOUT OUR TERMS & PRIVACY
Terms: https://terms.bilo.ba
Privacy policy: https://privacy.bilo.ba


If you have any questions, feel free to send us an email at hello@bilo.ba

descriptionHtml:
Biloba is the 1st Pediatrics On-Demand app that connects all parents to a pediatrician without appointment, any day and by instant messaging. They can ask all the questions they have regarding their children, in addition to the traditional medical follow-up.

HOW DOES IT WORK?
Biloba's messaging works like any traditional instant messaging app: parents write down their questions, and in less than 10 minutes a doctor or nurse take them in charge and will provide them with reliable and personalized answers.
Please note, Biloba is not an emergency service. In case of emergency, call 112.

WHEN AND WHY CAN WE USE BILOBA?
All parents have questions about their kids health and development.  For all these questions, Biloba provides them with a team of general practitioners, pediatricians and nurses, every day from 8 a.m. to 10 p.m.

For instance, it’s possible to use Biloba if your child has a fever, a headache, a stomach ache, reflux or pimples.
But it can also be practical questions about:
- food diversification,
- your baby's breastfeeding,
- your child's sleep,
- the evolution of your child's weight and height,
- a burn,
- a treatment follow-up,
- questions about a vaccine,
- the little daily worries...

If you have any doubt before asking your question, please remember that above all there are no silly questions, and that other parents have undoubtedly asked them before you.
We are here to help you. Feel free to ask anything you have in mind.

Biloba is the 1st on-demand pediatrics app that connects all parents to a pediatrician without appointment, any day and by instant messaging. They can ask all the questions they have regarding their children, in addition to the traditional medical follow-up.

HOW DOES IT WORK?
Biloba's messaging works like any traditional instant messaging app: parents write down their questions, and in less than 10 minutes a doctor or nurse take them in charge and will provide them with reliable and personalized answers.
Please note, Biloba is not an emergency service. In case of emergency, call 112.

WHEN AND WHY CAN WE USE BILOBA?
All parents have questions about their kids health and development. For all these questions, Biloba provides them with a team of general practitioners, pediatricians and nurses, every day from 8 a.m. to 10 p.m.

For instance, it’s possible to use Biloba if your child has a fever, a headache, a stomach ache, reflux or pimples.
But it can also be practical questions about:
- food diversification,
- your baby's breastfeeding,
- your child's sleep,
- the evolution of your child's weight and height,
- a burn,
- a treatment follow-up,
- questions about a vaccine,
- the little daily worries...

If you have any doubt before asking your question, please remember that above all there are no silly questions, and that other parents have undoubtedly asked them before you.
We are here to help you. Feel free to ask anything you have in mind.

WHAT ARE BILOBA'S KEY FEATURES?
With the Biloba app you can:
- Talk to our medical team 7 days a week, from 8 a.m to 10 p.m,
- Send pictures and videos,
- Use one and only subscription plan for all of your children,
- Talk to our medical team wherever you are, whatever you’re doing,
- Get a prescription if needed (only accepted in France).

SUBSCRIPTION PRICING AND TERMS
Biloba offers you automatically renewed subscriptions giving you unlimited access to its services. A medical team will be by your side during the chosen period, and you will be able to consult for all your children. No commitment: you can cancel anytime.

The rates apply to subscribers in the European Union. It may vary for other countries and actual charges may need to be converted to your local currency depending on your country of residence.
The subscription will automatically renew unless it is deactivated in your Store account settings at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.
You can go to your Play Store account settings to manage your subscription and turn off auto-renewal. Your Store account will be charged when the purchase is confirmed.

READ MORE ABOUT OUR TERMS & PRIVACY
Terms: https://terms.biloba.com
Privacy policy: https://privacy.biloba.com

If you have any questions, feel free to send us an email at hello@biloba.com

Biloba's messaging works like any traditional instant messaging app: parents write down their questions, and in less than 10 minutes a doctor or nurse take them in charge and will provide them with reliable and personalized answers.
Please note, Biloba is not an emergency service. In case of emergency, call 112.

WHEN AND WHY CAN WE USE BILOBA?
All parents have questions about their kids health and development. For all these questions, Biloba provides them with a team of general practitioners, pediatricians and nurses, every day from 8 a.m. to 10 p.m.

For instance, it’s possible to use Biloba if your child has a fever, a headache, a stomach ache, reflux or pimples.
But it can also be practical questions about:
- food diversification,
- your baby's breastfeeding,
- your child's sleep,
- the evolution of your child's weight and height,
- a burn,
- a treatment follow-up,
- questions about a vaccine,
- the little daily worries...

If you have any doubt before asking your question, please remember that above all there are no silly questions, and that other parents have undoubtedly asked them before you.
We are here to help you. Feel free to ask anything you have in mind.

WHAT ARE BILOBA'S KEY FEATURES?
With the Biloba app you can:
- Talk to our medical team 7 days a week, from 8 a.m to 10 p.m,
- Send pictures and videos,
- Use one and only subscription plan for all of your children,
- Talk to our medical team wherever you are, whatever you’re doing,
- Get a prescription if needed (only accepted in France).

SUBSCRIPTION PRICING AND TERMS
Biloba offers you automatically renewed subscriptions giving you unlimited access to its services. A medical team will be by your side during the chosen period, and you will be able to consult for all your children. No commitment: you can cancel anytime.

The rates apply to subscribers in the European Union. It may vary for other countries and actual charges may need to be converted to your local currency depending on your country of residence.
The subscription will automatically renew unless it is deactivated in your Store account settings at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.
You can go to your Play Store account settings to manage your subscription and turn off auto-renewal. Your Store account will be charged when the purchase is confirmed.

title: Biloba - On-demand pediatrics

creator: Biloba
descriptionHtml:
Biloba is the 1st on-demand pediatrics app that connects all parents to a pediatrician without appointment, any day and by instant messaging. They can ask all the questions they have regarding their children, in addition to the traditional medical follow-up.

HOW DOES IT WORK?
Biloba's messaging works like any traditional instant messaging app: parents write down their questions, and in less than 10 minutes a doctor or nurse take them in charge and will provide them with reliable and personalized answers.
Please note, Biloba is not an emergency service. In case of emergency, call 112.

WHEN AND WHY CAN WE USE BILOBA?
All parents have questions about their kids health and development. For all these questions, Biloba provides them with a team of general practitioners, pediatricians and nurses, every day from 8 a.m. to 10 p.m.

For instance, it’s possible to use Biloba if your child has a fever, a headache, a stomach ache, reflux or pimples.
But it can also be practical questions about:
- food diversification,
- your baby's breastfeeding,
- your child's sleep,
- the evolution of your child's weight and height,
- a burn,
- a treatment follow-up,
- questions about a vaccine,
- the little daily worries...

If you have any doubt before asking your question, please remember that above all there are no silly questions, and that other parents have undoubtedly asked them before you.
We are here to help you. Feel free to ask anything you have in mind.

WHAT ARE BILOBA'S KEY FEATURES?
With the Biloba app you can:
- Talk to our medical team 7 days a week, from 8 a.m to 10 p.m,
- Send pictures and videos,
- Use one and only subscription plan for all of your children,
- Talk to our medical team wherever you are, whatever you’re doing,
- Get a prescription if needed (only accepted in France).

SUBSCRIPTION PRICING AND TERMS
Biloba offers you automatically renewed subscriptions giving you unlimited access to its services. A medical team will be by your side during the chosen period, and you will be able to consult for all your children. No commitment: you can cancel anytime.

The rates apply to subscribers in the European Union. It may vary for other countries and actual charges may need to be converted to your local currency depending on your country of residence.
The subscription will automatically renew unless it is deactivated in your Store account settings at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.
You can go to your Play Store account settings to manage your subscription and turn off auto-renewal. Your Store account will be charged when the purchase is confirmed.

Privacy policy: https://privacy.biloba.com

title: Biloba - On-demand pediatrics

creator: Biloba
descriptionHtml:
Biloba is the 1st on-demand pediatrics app that connects all parents to a pediatrician without appointment, any day and by instant messaging. They can ask all the questions they have regarding their children, in addition to the traditional medical follow-up.

HOW DOES IT WORK?
Biloba's messaging works like any traditional instant messaging app: parents write down their questions, and in less than 10 minutes a doctor or nurse take them in charge and will provide them with reliable and personalized answers.
Please note, Biloba is not an emergency service. In case of emergency, call 112.

WHEN AND WHY CAN WE USE BILOBA?
All parents have questions about their kids health and development. For all these questions, Biloba provides them with a team of general practitioners, pediatricians and nurses, every day from 8 a.m. to 10 p.m.

For instance, it’s possible to use Biloba if your child has a fever, a headache, a stomach ache, reflux or pimples.
But it can also be practical questions about:
- food diversification,
- your baby's breastfeeding,
- your child's sleep,
- the evolution of your child's weight and height,
- a burn,
- a treatment follow-up,
- questions about a vaccine,

- Use one and only subscription plan for all of your children,
- Talk to our medical team wherever you are, whatever you’re doing,
- Get a prescription if needed (only accepted in France).

SUBSCRIPTION PRICING AND TERMS
Biloba offers you automatically renewed subscriptions giving you unlimited access to its services. A medical team will be by your side during the chosen period, and you will be able to consult for all your children. No commitment: you can cancel anytime.

title: Biloba - On-demand pediatrics

Biloba's messaging works like any traditional instant messaging app: parents write down their questions, and in less than 10 minutes a nurse or a doctor take them in charge and will provide them with reliable and personalized answers.
Please note, Biloba is not an emergency service. In case of emergency, call 112.

Biloba is the 1st on-demand pediatrics app that connects all parents to a pediatric medical team without appointment, any day and by instant messaging. They can ask all the questions they have regarding their children, in addition to the traditional medical follow-up.

HOW DOES IT WORK?
Biloba's messaging works like any traditional instant messaging app: parents write down their questions, and in less than 10 minutes a nurse or a doctor take them in charge and will provide them with reliable and personalized answers.

WHEN AND WHY CAN WE USE BILOBA?
All parents have questions about their kids health and development. For all these questions, Biloba provides them with a team of nurses, general practitioners and pediatricians, every day from 8am to 10pm.

For instance, it’s possible to use Biloba if your child has a fever, a headache, a stomach ache, reflux or pimples.
But it can also be practical questions about:
- food diversification,
- your baby's breastfeeding,
- your child's sleep,
- the evolution of your child's weight and height,
- a burn,
- a treatment follow-up,
- questions about a vaccine,
- the little daily worries...

If you have any doubt before asking your question, please remember that above all there are no silly questions, and that other parents have undoubtedly asked them before you.
We are here to help you. Feel free to ask anything you have in mind.

WHAT ARE BILOBA'S KEY FEATURES?
With the Biloba app you can:
- Talk to our medical team 7 days a week, from 8am to 10pm,
- Send pictures and videos,
- Use one and only subscription plan for all of your children,
- Talk to our medical team wherever you are, whatever you’re doing,
- Get a prescription if needed (only accepted in France),
- Access the medical report of your consultation written by our medical team.
- New!
• Track your child's growth thanks to a unique adding and viewing measures feature,
• Stay up to date with your child's vaccination records, and get push notification for the next scheduled one.

SUBSCRIPTION PRICING AND TERMS
Biloba offers you automatically renewed subscriptions giving you unlimited access to its services. A medical team will be by your side during the chosen period, and you will be able to consult for all your children. No commitment: you can cancel anytime.

The rates apply to subscribers in the European Union. It may vary for other countries and actual charges may need to be converted to your local currency depending on your country of residence.
The subscription will automatically renew unless it is deactivated in your Store account settings at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.
You can go to your Play Store account settings to manage your subscription and turn off auto-renewal. Your Store account will be charged when the purchase is confirmed.

READ MORE ABOUT OUR TERMS & PRIVACY
Terms: https://terms.biloba.com
Privacy policy: https://privacy.biloba.com

If you have any questions, feel free to send us an email at hello@biloba.com

title: Biloba - On-demand pediatrics

creator: Biloba
descriptionHtml:
Biloba is the 1st on-demand pediatrics app that connects all parents to a pediatric medical team without appointment by instant messaging. They can ask all the questions they have regarding their children, in addition to the traditional medical follow-up.

HOW DOES IT WORK?
Biloba's messaging works like any traditional instant messaging app: parents write down their questions, and in less than 10 minutes a nurse or a doctor take them in charge and will provide them with reliable and personalized answers.

WHEN AND WHY CAN WE USE BILOBA?
All parents have questions about their kids health and development. For all these questions, Biloba provides them with a team of nurses, general practitioners and pediatricians.

For instance, it’s possible to use Biloba if your child has a fever, a headache, a stomach ache, reflux or pimples.
But it can also be practical questions about:
- food diversification,
- your baby's breastfeeding,
- your child's sleep,
- the evolution of your child's weight and height,
- a burn,
- a treatment follow-up,
- questions about a vaccine,
- the little daily worries...

If you have any doubt before asking your question, please remember that above all there are no silly questions, and that other parents have undoubtedly asked them before you.
We are here to help you. Feel free to ask anything you have in mind.
